<style>
    .masonry-container, ui-card-panel > div, ui-card-panel:first-child > div > div {
        height: 100% !important;
        min-height: unset !important;
        max-height: unset !important;
    }
    
    ui-card-panel {
        height: calc(100% - 14px) !important;
    }
    
    ui-card-panel:first-child > div {
        display: flex !important;
        flex-direction: column !important;
    }

    .nr-dashboard-cardpanel > p {
        margin-right: 12px!important;
        text-align: center!important;
    }
    
    ui-card-panel:first-child > div > div {
        flex-grow: 1 !important;
    }

    ui-card-panel:first-child > div > div > md-card {
        height: auto !important;
    }

    div.ui-svg {
        display: grid !important;
        place-items: center !important;
    }

    div.ui-svg svg {
        max-height: 100% !important;
    }

    .plant-tank-level-chart {
        position: relative !important;
    }

    .plant-tank-level-chart::before, .plant-tank-level-chart::after {
        content: "Full" !important;
        position: absolute !important;
        top: 20% !important;
        left: 0 !important;
        bottom: 15% !important;
        width: 12% !important;
        font-size: 75% !important;
        text-align: right !important;
        background-color: white !important;
        user-select: none !important;
    }

    .plant-tank-level-chart::after {
        content: "Empty" !important;
        top: unset !important;
        bottom: 17% !important;
    }

    .security:fullscreen {
        background-color: white !important;
    }

    .security:fullscreen .nr-dashboard-cardcontainer > :not(.camera-stream):not(.camera-stream-controls) {
        display: none !important;
    }

    .security:fullscreen > * {
        width: 100% !important;
        height: auto !important;
    }

    .camera-stream {
        width: 100% !important;
        height: unset !important;
    }

    .security:fullscreen .camera-stream img {
        max-height: calc(100vh - 7em) !important;
        cursor: zoom-out !important;
    }

    .camera-stream img {
        aspect-ratio: 3/2 !important;
        object-fit: contain !important;
        background-color: #EEE !important;
        cursor: zoom-in !important;
    }

    .camera-stream-controls {
        display: flex !important;
        flex-direction: row !important;
        justify-content: center !important;
        gap: .5em !important;
        width: calc(100% - 12px) !important;
        height: auto !important;
        padding: 0 !important;
        margin: 0 6px !important;
        background-color: var(--nr-dashboard-pageTitlebarBackgroundColor, #0003) !important;
        overflow: hidden !important;
    }

    .security:fullscreen .camera-stream-controls {
        position: fixed !important;
        top: unset !important;
        bottom: 6px !important;
    }

    .camera-stream-controls button {
        position: relative !important;
        width: 2em !important;
        height: 2em !important;
        color: transparent !important;
        overflow: hidden !important;
        border: none !important;
        border-radius: 0 !important;
        background-color: #0000 !important;
        transition: background-color .3s !important;
        user-select: none !important;
    }

    .camera-stream-controls button:hover {
        background-color: #0003 !important;
    }
    
    .camera-stream-controls button::before {
        content: attr(data-content) !important;
        position: absolute !important;
        top: 0 !important;
        left: 0 !important;
        right: 0 !important;
        bottom: 0 !important;
        display: grid !important;
        place-items: center !important;
        color: white !important;
        line-height: 1em !important;
        font-weight: bold !important;
        user-select: none !important;
    }

    .log {
        height: 5em !important;
        overflow-y: auto !important;
    }

    .log > p {
        font-weight: bold !important;
    }

    .settings .nr-dashboard-cardcontainer {
        width: auto !important;
        height: auto !important;
        flex-grow: 1 !important;
    }

    .settings .nr-dashboard-cardcontainer > md-card {
        width: 100% !important;
        height: auto !important;
    }

    .plant-light-time-text .label {
        margin: revert !important;
    }
</style>
